WEBVTT

00:00:01.240 --> 00:00:02.660
Help me cook.

00:00:03.240 --> 00:00:04.100
Pham Hien

00:00:04.840 --> 00:00:07.920
Thanks for not just making me the leader of the Beg cult.

00:00:07.920 --> 00:00:09.660
And save the Cult from fire and water.

00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:13.240
But the second floor of Truong Sinh was already taken away by Duong Le.

00:00:13.240 --> 00:00:14.580
I can't find it.

00:00:14.600 --> 00:00:15.740
What do you mean?

00:00:16.120 --> 00:00:17.860
Do you want me to help you?

00:00:18.280 --> 00:00:19.300
But that's okay.

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:22.140
I got the real thing from the room south of Jia.

00:00:23.360 --> 00:00:24.160
I think so.

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:27.580
Mr. Phuong, why don't I promise myself?

00:00:27.720 --> 00:00:30.000
Old Mao, this is revenge.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:30.980
No need.

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:37.220
If not, can you tell me about To Truong Tung's world?

00:00:37.400 --> 00:00:40.300
To Truong Tung doesn't like women?

00:00:40.480 --> 00:00:44.420
It seems that if he wants to stay, he can only make this decision.

00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:00.500
Well, not that much.

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:13.320
It's not what you think.

00:01:13.320 --> 00:01:15.680
Don't get me wrong.

00:01:15.680 --> 00:01:17.120
You two go out.

00:01:17.120 --> 00:01:19.020
I need to talk to the governors.

00:01:20.480 --> 00:01:21.940
How did you find here?

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:24.580
I came to tell you some news.

00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:27.300
The leader claimed to be a man of Brown village.

00:01:27.640 --> 00:01:31.100
And said he wanted to take revenge on the entire martial arts world in Brown village.

00:01:31.240 --> 00:01:32.540
Who helped him take revenge?

00:01:32.800 --> 00:01:35.020
Who did he give his complete eldest grandson to?

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:37.620
Brown Village never heard of it.

00:01:37.840 --> 00:01:40.640
Where? What did you say his name was?

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:43.480
The leader of the Demonic Cult is named Pham Quang.

00:01:43.480 --> 00:01:44.280
What?

00:01:44.880 --> 00:01:46.260
She said his name was Pham Quang.

00:01:48.560 --> 00:01:50.940
Is my father still alive?